## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-210">一个类派生自<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.TaskScheduler>为了支持与调试器集成实现此方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-210">A class derived from <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.TaskScheduler> implements this method in order to support integration with debuggers.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-211">调试器请求访问数据时，此方法仅调用由.NET Framework 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-211">This method will only be invoked by the .NET Framework when the debugger requests access to the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-212">将遍历的调试实用程序来访问任务的可枚举项返回当前排队到此计划程序，使调试器能够提供此信息在用户界面中的表示形式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-212">The enumerable returned will be traversed by debugging utilities to access the tasks currently queued to this scheduler, enabling the debugger to provide a representation of this information in the user interface.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-213">请务必注意，调用此方法时，此进程中的所有其他线程会被冻结。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-213">It is important to note that, when this method is called, all other threads in the process will be frozen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-214">因此，很重要，可以避免与其他线程同步，这可能导致阻塞。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-214">Therefore, it's important to avoid synchronization with other threads that may lead to blocking.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-215">如果同步是必需的并且你将无法获取锁在这种方法，然后应引发异常，以便调试器不会阻止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-215">If synchronization is necessary, and you are unable to acquire the lock in this method, then you should throw an exception so that the debugger does not block.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-216">下面的示例显示了 C# 中的一种可行方法：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-216">The following example shows one possible approach in C#:</span></span>
  
```csharp
protected override IEnumerable<Task> GetScheduledTasks()  
{  
    bool lockTaken = false;  
    try  
    {  
        Monitor.TryEnter(_syncObj, ref lockTaken);  
        if (lockTaken)  
        {  
            return _tasks.ToArray();  
        }  
        else throw new NotSupportedException();  
    }  
    finally  
    {  
    if (lockTaken) Monitor.Exit(_syncObj);  
    }}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-217">此外，此方法，并返回可枚举不能修改任何全局可见状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-217">Additionally, this method and the enumerable returned must not modify any globally visible state.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-218">返回可枚举应永远不会为 null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-218">The returned enumerable should never be null.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-219">如果当前没有排队的任务，应改为返回空的可枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-219">If there are currently no queued tasks, an empty enumerable should be returned instead.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-220">开发人员要实现自定义调试器不应直接调用此方法，但应使用的内部包装方法`GetScheduledTasksForDebugger`改为： `internal Task[] GetScheduledTasksForDebugger()`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-220">Developers who are implementing custom debuggers shouldn't call this method directly, but should use the internal wrapper method `GetScheduledTasksForDebugger` instead: `internal Task[] GetScheduledTasksForDebugger()`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-221">此包装器方法返回任务而不是一个可枚举对象的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-221">This wrapper method returns an array of tasks instead of an enumerable.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-222">若要检索活动计划程序的列表，请使用内部方法`internal static TaskScheduler[] GetTaskSchedulersForDebugger()`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-222">To retrieve a list of active schedulers, use the internal method `internal static TaskScheduler[] GetTaskSchedulersForDebugger()`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-223">此静态方法返回的所有活动数组<xref:System.Threading.Tasks.TaskScheduler>实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-223">This static method returns an array of all active <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.TaskScheduler> instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e31fe-224">然后，可以使用`GetScheduledTasksForDebugger`上每个计划程序实例要检索其计划的任务的列表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e31fe-224">You can then use `GetScheduledTasksForDebugger` on each scheduler instance to retrieve its list of scheduled tasks.</span></span>
